7. Checklist Before Creating PR
[ ] Branch name follows convention (feature/be- or fix/fe-, etc.)
[ ] Commit messages follow format (type(scope): subject)
[ ] Code is tested locally
[ ] No sensitive data (passwords, keys) committed
[ ] PR description is clear and complete
[ ] Assigned correct reviewer (sub-team leader)
